com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker

Class Subject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.Subject

  • public class Subject
extends java.lang.Object
    An object for managing extra event decoration. All the properties are optional. However, the timezone is set by default, to that of the server.
